service: foodmind-backend

provider:
  name: aws
  runtime: python3.12
  region: ap-southeast-1

functions:
  auth:
    handler: auth/main.lambda_handler
    events:
      - httpApi:
          path: /auth/register
          method: post
      - httpApi:
          path: /auth/login
          method: post
      - httpApi:
          path: /auth/confirm
          method: post
      - httpApi:
          path: /auth/resend-otp
          method: post
      - httpApi:
          path: /auth/forgot-password
          method: post

plugins:
  - serverless-python-requirements
